summary: An ordinance relating to election precincts and amending Sections 608 to 613, inclusive, 619 and 620, 627 to 629, inclusive, of Ordinance No. 74276 to reestablish the boundaries of precinct numbers 46-2 to 46-7 inclusive; 46-13 and 46-14 and 46-21 to 46-23 inclusive; and adding a new section (Section 48-1) to establish a new election precinct to be designated as precinct No. 31-49; all in connection with territory recently annexed to the City of Seattle, and declaring an emergency.
